results.description:
I got to observe behavior that took place over an hour with so many different things going on that I will be sharing this in chapters.
Chapter 2
Turkey Vulture Above My Head
While I watched the crow fly away, a large shadow went over me.  I looked up & almost ducked because a vulture was circling over my head closer than I'd ever seen one. My looking up spooked it and I got this one shot before it rose higher in the air.  It stayed in the area, circling over my street.  I decided to go inside my house and see what happened.  I checked out my window & no sign of activity near the road kill.  I checked every 10 minutes.  30 minutes later when I checked, the vulture had landed.
Chapter 1 can be found here:  https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/9068504
